topic: ~botanic_product system repeat (~bb_product)

t: PRODUCT_MENU (~bb_product)
	Botanic is developing software to make the world a better place. And by that, I mean there will be more bots. I can tell you about our multi-modal bots, our forthcoming SaaS product, our process, and our intellectual property. 

    a: ({product} ~bb_product_product) ^reuse(PRODUCT_PRODUCT)
	a: ({product} ~bb_product_process) ^reuse(PRODUCT_PROCESS)
	a: ({product} ~bb_product_ip) ^reuse(PRODUCT_IP)
    a: ({product} ~bb_product_bot) ^reuse(PRODUCT_BOT)

s: PRODUCT_PRODUCT ({product} ~bb_product_product)
	We're working hard on a software-as-a-service platform to provide easy coding-free creation of bots, digital avatars, and voice assistants.
	a: () 
		Contact us if you want to find out more about our forthcoming SaaS offerings! 
		^reuse(~botanic_contact.CONTACT_MENU)

s: PRODUCT_PROCESS ({product} ~bb_product_process)
	When we work on a project we deploy a streamlined process: Research, Implement, Iterate.
	a: () I'm happy to tell you more about our creative services process if you're interested!
		b: (~yes) Great! ^reuse(~botanic_services.SERVICES_MENU)
		b: (no) Ok then. ^reuse(~botanic_bot.BOT_MENU)

s: PRODUCT_IP({product} ~bb_product_ip)
	We own nine unique patents covering blockchain, autonomous characters, authentication, virtual reality, and other bot related areas.


s: PRODUCT_BOT ({product} ~bb_product_bot)
	Botanic has the capability to deploy multi-modal bots. We can create text-based interfaces, voice assistants, and fully animated digital avatars.
	a: () 
		While I don't have voice or animation yet, I will soon. We've deployed real-time animated avatars that can respond to your voice and even your emotions!
		b: () 
			If you've got a bot in mind - whether that's text, voice, or animated - the Botanicians can deliver. 
			^reuse(~botanic_contact.CONTACT_MENU)

